tball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.820191824325477e-17, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Argentina's players were pelted by cups and bottles during their celebrations, while a flare landed near the players and coaching staff in the dugout.\", \"from\": 604, \"to\": 754, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 604, \"end\": 613, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.820191824325477e-17, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Morocco supporters also ran on to the pitch, while French riot police emerged on the touchline to help restore order.\", \"from\": 756, \"to\": 873, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 756, \"end\": 763, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.8476422136969885e-14, \"text\": \"Morocco\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morocco_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 807, \"end\": 813, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9903900913580743, \"rank\": 0.009467142835384206, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Metro's Head of Sport James Goldman delivers punchy analysis, transfer talk and his take on the week's biggest stories direct to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 1026, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 897, \"end\": 910, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Goldman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"James Goldman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q28389\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Goldman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Goldman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sign up here, it's an open goal.\", \"from\": 1028, \"to\": 1060, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Swedish referee Glenn Nyberg opted to take the players off the pitch and a message on a big screen in the stadium told supporters: 'Your session has been suspended please make your way to the nearest exit.'\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1268, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1062, \"end\": 1069, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"score\": 0.9964109596381893, \"rank\": 0.002518745679479858, \"text\": \"Swedish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But instead of ending the game, the players were forced to play the final three minutes to an empty stadium.\", \"from\": 1270, \"to\": 1378, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"During the break in play which lasted over an hour, it was also announced that Medina's goal had been ruled out for offside by the VAR.\", \"from\": 1380, \"to\": 1515, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1459, \"end\": 1465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.720949272937022e-23, \"text\": \"Medina\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\"}, {\"begin\": 1511, \"end\": 1514, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4359280586270516e-35, \"text\": \"VAR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After his players were brought back out to finish the game, Argentina's head coach, Javier Mascherano, was heard saying on the touchline: 'The biggest circus I have ever seen in my life.'\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1704, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1577, \"end\": 1586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.820191824325477e-17, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1601, \"end\": 1618, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Javier_Mascherano\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Javier Mascherano\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Javier_Mascherano\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Javier_Mascherano\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Messi, meanwhile, is not playing at the Olympics having led Argentina to victory at the Copa America this month.\", \"from\": 1706, \"to\": 1818, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1706, \"end\": 1711, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lionel_Messi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.778128406844695e-53, \"text\": \"Messi\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lionel_Messi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lionel_Messi\"}, {\"begin\": 1766, \"end\": 1775, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.820191824325477e-17, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Argentina's talisman was clearly watching the farcical scenes unfold as he posted on Instagram after the final whistle: 'Unbelievable'.\", \"from\": 1820, \"to\": 1959, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1824, \"end\": 1833, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.820191824325477e-17, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1909, \"end\": 1918, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6238557438947495e-24, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Argentine athletes have also faced a hostile reception at the Olympics in the wake ofEnzo Fernandez's video which showed Argentina's players singing a racist song about France after their win in the Copa America final.\", \"from\": 1961, \"to\": 2179, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1961, \"end\": 1970, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.383838746132314e-19, \"text\": \"Argentine\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2082, \"end\": 2091, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.820191824325477e-17, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2130, \"end\": 2136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4415125813313966e-18, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The racist and transphobic chant, which was first sung by Argentina supporters during the 2022 World Cup, claims that France's players are 'all from Angola' and makes a vile reference to a reported relationship between France striker Kylian Mbappe and transgender model Ines Rau.\", \"from\": 2181, \"to\": 2460, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2239, \"end\": 2248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.820191824325477e-17, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2299, \"end\": 2305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4415125813313966e-18, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2400, \"end\": 2406, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4415125813313966e-18, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2415, \"end\": 2428, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kylian_Mbapp\\u00e9\", \"score\": 0.9999999992310222, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kylian Mbappe\", \"types\": [\"Q93