ource/Kenya_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The truth is that I was surprised, I did not know it was going to be so much,' Santiago Alvarez, a member of Argentina's Rugby Sevens squad, told TyC Sports.\", \"from\": 2685, \"to\": 2842, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2764, \"end\": 2780, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santiago_\\u00c1lvarez_(general)\", \"score\": 0.7312131577028318, \"rank\": 0.3675889328064228, \"text\": \"Santiago Alvarez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santiago_\\u00c1lvarez_(general)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santiago_\\u00c1lvarez_(general)\"}, {\"begin\": 2794, \"end\": 2803, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.820191824325477e-17, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2806, \"end\": 2818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rugby_sevens\", \"score\": 0.9999993437629534, \"rank\": 6.562376076195011e-07, \"text\": \"Rugby Sevens\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rugby_sevens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rugby_sevens\"}, {\"begin\": 2831, \"end\": 2841, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TyC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9999999899337126, \"rank\": 1.0066403093925667e-08, \"text\": \"TyC Sports\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TyC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TyC_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'But that's also nice.\", \"from\": 2844, \"to\": 2866, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The same thing happens in Argentina, the French are very similar to us in that sense, they are very passionate.\", \"from\": 2867, \"to\": 2978, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2893, \"end\": 2902, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.820191824325477e-17, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2908, \"end\": 2914, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9903900913580743, \"rank\": 0.009467142835384206, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's one more thing.\", \"from\": 2979, \"to\": 2999, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But well, we have to abstract ourselves from that and think about ourselves.'\", \"from\": 3000, \"to\": 3077, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 3079, \"to\": 3127, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 3129, \"to\": 3199, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:All the scandals that have rocked the Paris 2024 Olympics before it's even started  ArrowMORE:Team GB star explains why she's snubbing Paris Olympics opening ceremony  ArrowMORE:Classy Carlos Alcaraz and Iga Swiatek will follow their French Open triumphs by striking Olympic gold in Paris  Sign up and tell us which team you support to get personalised updates about your club.\", \"from\": 3201, \"to\": 3588, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3346, \"end\": 3360, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\":